CHINA FUELS MURKY CETACEAN TRADE IN RUSSIA

15 ORCAS AND MORE THAN 200 BELUGAS WERE SOLD TO AQUARIUMS IN CHINA IN THE
LAST 5 YEARS.

BOTH BELUGAS AND ORCAS ARE HIGHLY SOCIABLE ANIMALS

It is deeply traumatic for them to be separated from their families.
