RUSSIA IS THE ONLY COUNTRY IN THE WORLD THAT STILL CAPTURES ORCAS AND BELUGAS
FOR AQUARIUMS

THE EXACT PRICE TAG IS UNKNOWN,
BUT QUOTES RANGE FROM 1 MILLION DOLLARS FOR BELUGA WHALE
AND FROM 6 TO 10 MILLION DOLLARS FOR ORCA

KREMLIN CALLED THE "WHALE PRISON"SITUATION APPALLING

RUSSIAN OFFICIALS HAVE LAUNCHED AN INVESTIGATION AND OPENED CRIMINAL CASE,
BUT AN ORDER TO RELEASE THE ANIMALS HAVEN'T BEEN MADE YET

